capture \= cv2\.VideoCapture\(path\)
 capture\.set\(cv2\.CAP_PROP_POS_FRAMES\, start\)

 n_width \= 50
 n_height \= 50
 length \= end \- start

 images \= np\.zeros\(shape\=\(length\, n_width\, n_height\, 3\)\, dtype\=np\.uint8\)
 for i in range\(length\)\:
 sign_progress\(i / length\)
 capture\.set\(cv2\.CAP_PROP_POS_FRAMES\, float\(i \* resolution\)\)
 ret\, frame \= capture\.read\(\)
 col \= np\.mean\(frame\, axis \= \(0\, 1\)\)
 images\[i\, \:\, \:\] \= col

 columns \= np\.ceil\(length / per_row\)
 final \= np\.zeros\(shape\=\(per_row \* n_width\, columns \* n_height\, 3\)\, dtype\=np\.uint8\)

 counter \= 0
 for i in range\(columns\)\:
 for j in range\(per_row\)\:
 final\[j \* n_width\: j \* n_width \+ n_width\,
 i \* n_height\: i \* n_height \+ n_height\] \= images\[counter\]

 result \= dict\(
 mosaic\=final
 \)
